title: AfroPunk Reimagined - A Bonus Episode Sponsored By Target
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary: A bonus episode of #TheFriendZone in partnership with Target. We discussed the best emerging artists at AfroPunk over the years. Favs we were excited to experience in person. Top hair, makeup and fashion moments. Our meet + greets. Most memorable experiences overall. And we curate our dream AfroPunk cities, lineups and stage sets.
